----------------------------- MODULE Consensus ------------------------------
EXTENDS Sets, TLAPS
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
CONSTANT Value  
VARIABLE chosen 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Init == chosen = {}

Next == 
    /\ chosen = {}
    /\ \E v \in Value : chosen' = {v}

Spec == Init /\ [][Next]_chosen
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Inv == 
    /\ chosen \subseteq Value
    /\ IsFiniteSet(chosen)
    /\ Cardinality(chosen) \leq 1
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
THEOREM Invariance == Spec => []Inv
  PROOF OMITTED

=============================================================================
